1
00:00:28,080 --> 00:00:29,032
Ranya

2
00:00:36,140 --> 00:00:40,712
Happy birthday to you Happy birthday to you

3
00:00:41,380 --> 00:00:45,680
Happy birthday to you Happy birthday to you

4
00:00:46,380 --> 00:00:51,800
Happy birthday  Happy birthday

5
00:00:53,000 --> 00:00:57,504
Happy birthday to you

6
00:00:59,700 --> 00:01:00,736
Make a wish.

7
00:01:07,830 --> 00:01:10,816
I wish for us to love each other forever.

8
00:01:13,710 --> 00:01:15,896
You’re not supposed to say it out loud!

9
00:01:15,936 --> 00:01:17,760
Otherwise, the wish won’t come

10
00:01:19,700 --> 00:01:23,288
It will definitely come true,as long as we work on it together.

11
00:01:29,940 --> 00:01:31,088
Can I eat it now?

12
00:01:33,536 --> 00:01:35,540
Which part would you like to start with?

13
00:01:49,312 --> 00:01:50,648
I’ll start right here.

14
00:03:47,430 --> 00:03:50,264
You know, Ranya... you are the best gift I’ve ever received.

15
00:03:54,310 --> 00:03:57,688
Thank you for loving me.

16
00:04:03,100 --> 00:04:04,104
So...

17
00:04:09,190 --> 00:04:13,168
can I unwrap this gift now?

18
00:09:45,830 --> 00:09:48,362
Cheers!

19
00:09:51,000 --> 00:09:55,754
Officially congratulations to our President!

20
00:09:57,790 --> 00:10:01,570
And congratulations to you too, Ranya.

21
00:10:03,674 --> 00:10:04,570
for what?

22
00:10:05,190 --> 00:10:10,186
For officially becoming a member of the Marketing Team!

23
00:10:10,740 --> 00:10:12,562
Both you and me.

24
00:10:13,100 --> 00:10:14,794
P'Chat! You never told me about this!

25
00:10:16,190 --> 00:10:16,914
Look!

26
00:10:17,720 --> 00:10:22,754
Oh! Oh! Ouch! That really hurts, my friend.

27
00:10:22,794 --> 00:10:24,946
How do you stop hurting?, friend?

28
00:10:24,978 --> 00:10:27,322
Well, if it hurts, you have to kiss it right here.

29
00:10:28,538 --> 00:10:30,540
No way! You're so devious.

30
00:10:39,710 --> 00:10:41,522
And what about us?

31
00:10:43,480 --> 00:10:44,418
What do you mean us?

32
00:10:45,430 --> 00:10:46,890
What do you mean us?

33
00:10:48,430 --> 00:10:51,050
Give her a kiss! Come on, kiss, kiss, kiss!

34
00:11:01,880 --> 00:11:07,602
Hey, actually... I really need to thank you and Ranya?

35
00:11:08,530 --> 00:11:09,722
Thank us for what?

36
00:11:10,778 --> 00:11:12,780
For making it possible for me to fall in love with Nutcha.

37
00:11:14,594 --> 00:11:16,306
Oh, here you go again!

38
00:11:16,338 --> 00:11:17,882
Wait... I haven't even said I accept your love yet!

39
00:11:18,280 --> 00:11:22,570
Oh... I wasn't asking for your opinion.

40
00:11:22,602 --> 00:11:24,018
This is a forced situation.

41
00:11:24,850 --> 00:11:29,498
I'm forcing you, and then I'll... I'll... What's the word?

42
00:11:31,310 --> 00:11:32,874
Hit me, hit me.

43
00:11:33,250 --> 00:11:34,666
It's wet, you know. Huh?

44
00:11:34,706 --> 00:11:36,670
Ah ah ah, here, take it again, take it again, come

45
00:11:37,570 --> 00:11:40,106
Alright, alright, let's just toast to that! Come on!

46
00:11:40,378 --> 00:11:42,380
Cheers!

47
00:12:27,860 --> 00:12:29,354
Mom, don't you worry about me anymore.

48
00:12:31,190 --> 00:12:33,250
I'm so happy these days.

49
00:12:36,146 --> 00:12:38,150
I have amazing friends by my side,

50
00:12:41,070 --> 00:12:43,562
and I've finally become the Company President,

51
00:12:53,162 --> 00:12:57,794
From now on, I’m going to make our dream come true.

52
00:13:01,698 --> 00:13:03,700
I’ll give back to society and help people,

53
00:13:04,580 --> 00:13:07,434
just like you always told me to.

54
00:14:14,600 --> 00:14:19,658
This journal… I want it to be the memory

55
00:14:20,690 --> 00:14:22,874
of me and someone special

56
00:14:24,270 --> 00:14:28,210
of my first and only love.

57
00:14:34,930 --> 00:14:38,546
It’s been a year since we started dating.

58
00:14:39,080 --> 00:14:44,418
P'Thana is still as lovely as the very first day we met.

59
00:14:45,790 --> 00:14:49,562
I wish I could tell my father about us.

60
00:14:50,450 --> 00:14:55,218
I’m sure he would love P'Thana just as much as I do.

61
00:15:06,320 --> 00:15:10,482
P’Thana is gone. Gone forever.

62
00:15:12,434 --> 00:15:14,818
We promised we would get married,

63
00:15:15,820 --> 00:15:19,218
So why does fate have to be this cruel?

64
00:15:24,400 --> 00:15:25,770
I’m pregnant.

65
00:15:26,990 --> 00:15:29,194
This child is my baby...

66
00:15:29,860 --> 00:15:31,250
our baby.

67
00:15:50,714 --> 00:15:53,250
Father won’t let me give birth to this child,

68
00:15:54,370 --> 00:15:56,034
but I won’t give up.

69
00:16:01,750 --> 00:16:05,522
No matter what I have to do, I will bring this child into the world.

70
00:16:07,290 --> 00:16:11,970
Thana... I can do anything for the sake of our child.

71
00:16:52,830 --> 00:16:54,138
Dad, what are you saying?

72
00:16:54,670 --> 00:16:56,266
Mom and I love you more than anything.

73
00:16:56,960 --> 00:16:59,082
And you love us too, don’t you?

74
00:17:01,360 --> 00:17:03,514
I have never loved either of you.

75
00:18:32,370 --> 00:18:33,538
Are you feeling any better?

76
00:18:40,330 --> 00:18:42,018
Do you want to talk to me about it?

77
00:18:51,610 --> 00:18:53,314
I’ve always wondered

78
00:18:55,670 --> 00:18:59,402
why Dad hated Mom and me so much.

79
00:19:01,300 --> 00:19:03,482
At first, I thought he just didn't love Mom anymore...

80
00:19:05,790 --> 00:19:08,554
But after all, I was still his child.

81
00:19:12,100 --> 00:19:13,298
But that wasn’t it.

82
00:19:16,910 --> 00:19:18,634
I’m not his daughter.

83
00:19:24,114 --> 00:19:26,110
Now that I know the truth...

84
00:19:29,540 --> 00:19:35,922
I’m heartbroken, but at the same time, I’m so relieved.

85
00:19:38,070 --> 00:19:42,602
I’m crying for a man who isn’t even my father...

86
00:19:46,202 --> 00:19:47,226
Why is that?

87
00:19:50,100 --> 00:19:51,762
It’s okay

88
00:19:56,458 --> 00:19:58,460
I want you to know that

89
00:19:59,858 --> 00:20:02,426
There are two people who love you very, very much.

90
00:20:03,466 --> 00:20:06,298
And that's me and your Mom.

91
00:20:08,840 --> 00:20:10,970
The way your mother looked at you...

92
00:20:13,560 --> 00:20:15,346
it was always filled with nothing but love.

93
00:20:17,990 --> 00:20:22,914
you were truly born out of a very beautiful love.

94
00:20:27,370 --> 00:20:32,354
You're right. I really was born out of love.

95
00:20:35,710 --> 00:20:37,458
I love you

96
00:20:40,410 --> 00:20:41,834
I love you too.

97
00:21:13,300 --> 00:21:15,394
By now, Dad must have found Mom already.

98
00:21:19,470 --> 00:21:22,714
Please tell Mom for me that I’m doing well.

99
00:21:23,426 --> 00:21:24,562
She doesn't have to worry about me anymore.

100
00:21:33,250 --> 00:21:36,634
Hello. My name is Ranya,

101
00:21:38,546 --> 00:21:40,178
and I’m P’Pimchat’s girlfriend. Don't worry,

102
00:21:43,870 --> 00:21:47,298
I’ll be the one to take care of her from now on.

103
00:21:50,930 --> 00:21:52,610
Wait, are you proposing to me right now?

104
00:21:54,310 --> 00:21:55,858
You could say that.

105
00:21:57,410 --> 00:21:59,410
Once you ask, there's no returning me, okay?

106
00:22:00,570 --> 00:22:01,762
I’m not giving you back.

107
00:22:02,120 --> 00:22:03,946
I love you so much.

108
00:22:06,130 --> 00:22:07,794
Oh, you’re so adorable, I just want to pinch your cheeks!

109
00:22:09,790 --> 00:22:11,394
Is my girlfriend cute?

110
00:22:13,990 --> 00:22:16,866
I brought her here so you can finally meet her.

111
00:22:34,190 --> 00:22:37,410
What made you want to come stargazing tonight?

112
00:22:40,020 --> 00:22:41,698
I just wanted a change of scenery.

113
00:22:47,030 --> 00:22:52,506
And I was thinking... the day Mom first brought you into our lives,

114
00:22:54,120 --> 00:22:57,186
she probably just wanted to make sure I’d have someone by my side, exactly like I do right now.

115
00:22:59,258 --> 00:23:03,114
But Mom probably never imagined we’d actually fall in love.

116
00:23:05,858 --> 00:23:07,860
Maybe she did.

117
00:23:09,070 --> 00:23:10,250
Who knows?

118
00:23:16,250 --> 00:23:16,970
Ranya.

119
00:23:18,282 --> 00:23:19,122
Yes?

120
00:23:23,400 --> 00:23:25,010
Will you marry me?

121
00:23:29,460 --> 00:23:31,330
From this moment on, and for all of eternity...

122
00:23:33,140 --> 00:23:34,618
let's stay together.

123
00:23:37,250 --> 00:23:38,218
Yes.

124
00:23:38,910 --> 00:23:42,826
From now on, and for all of eternity, we will be together.
